parameters.name: bulk
parameters.description: This parameter specifies that bulk operation is being used in the query. This parameter is required for bulk rule operations.

parameters.name: insertAfter
parameters.description: This parameter specifies that the rules will be inserted after the specified rule index. If no section or category is specified, the rules will be added to the section or category after the insertion point. insertBefore takes precedence over insertAfter - if both are specified, the insertBefore parameter will apply.

parameters.name: insertBefore
parameters.description: This parameter specifies that the rules will be inserted before the specified rule index. parameters.description: This parameter specifies the section into which the rules will be added. If this parameter is not used the section will be the default section. Only 'mandatory' and 'default' are allowed values. If a section is specified, a category cannot be specified.

parameters.name: category
parameters.description: This parameter specifies the category into which the rules will be added. If a category is specified it must exist or the request will fail. If a section is specified, a category cannot be specified.
